posts.post_content:
Have these PSA 4 commons available for trade. Looking for other PSA 4 commons to upgrade my set. Have several I’m needing but here are my key ones I’m looking for:

Becker, Cassidy, Conroy fielding, Devlin, Donlin, Goode, Marshall, Myers batting, O’Hara NY, Pelty horizontal, Quinn, Schlei portrait, Wiltse port with cap, Young Irv

TRADED/SOLD: Stovall port, Krause, Lennox, Mattern, Stephens , Groom, Hoffman, Milan, Ritter

AVAILABLE: Schaefer, Summers

If you have any of these available for trade or sale, please let me know

Thanks
Jeff
